

SQL> --test order array element error
SQL> create table t_order_array_1(id number(5,5), c_int int[]);

Succeed.

SQL> select id, c_int from t_order_array_1 union all select id, c_int from t_order_array_1 order by id desc, c_int[2] + c_int[3] desc limit 1; -- error

OG-00601, Sql syntax error: ORDER BY item must be the number of a SELECT-list expression
