---------------------------------------- ------------

0 rows fetched.

SQL> select id, c_int[2] from t_order_array_1 union all select id, c_int[2] from t_order_array_1 order by id desc, c_int[3] desc limit 1; -- error

OG-00601, Sql syntax error: ORDER BY item must be the number of a SELECT-list expression
SQL> drop table if exists t_order_array_1;

Succeed.

